data.description: Transform this unique all-block home into your dream abode, surrounded by breathtaking mountain scenery. Boasting a private well and expansive workshop, this property offers ample opportunities for recreation and entertainment. Relax on one of the two patios while taking in the stunning mountain views, or gather with friends and family in the spacious great room with its magnificent stone fireplace. The wood-burning stove in the mstr bedroom provides warmth on chilly nights. The large kitchen and dining area are perfect for hosting gatherings, while the property sits on over half an acre of desert landscaped land. Two of the bedrooms need to be closed in and finished. FHA loan loan looks to be assumed/qualifying almost newer                                   larg capacity Washer and dryer
